[package]
name = "libspa"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Tom Wagner <tom.a.wagner@protonmail.com", "Guillaume Desmottes <guillaume.desmottes@collabora.com>",]
rust-version = "1.77"
edition = "2021"
categories = [ "api-bindings", "multimedia",]
description = "Rust bindings for libspa"
repository = "https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/pipewire/pipewire-rs"
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
homepage = "https://pipewire.org"
documentation = "https://pipewire.pages.freedesktop.org/pipewire-rs/libspa/"
keywords = [ "pipewire", "multimedia", "audio", "video",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2"
libc = "0.2"
nix = "0.27"
cookie-factory = "0.3.2"
nom = "7"
convert_case = "0.6"

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "6"
cc = "1.0.66"

[features]
v0_3_33 = []
v0_3_40 = [ "v0_3_33",]
v0_3_65 = [ "v0_3_40", "spa_sys/v0_3_65",]
v0_3_75 = [ "v0_3_65",]

[dependencies.spa_sys]
package = "libspa-sys"
version = "0.8"
path = "../libspa-sys"

[dev-dependencies.pipewire-sys]
version = "0.8"
path = "../pipewire-sys"

[dev-dependencies.pipewire]
version = "0.8"
path = "../pipewire"

[package.metadata.system-deps.libspa]
name = "libspa-0.2"
version = "0.2"

[package]
name = "libspa-sys"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Tom Wagner <tom.a.wagner@protonmail.com", "Guillaume Desmottes <guillaume.desmottes@collabora.com>",]
rust-version = "1.77"
edition = "2021"
links = "libspa-0.2"
categories = [ "api-bindings", "multimedia",]
description = "Rust FFI bindings for libspa"
repository = "https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/pipewire/pipewire-rs"
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
homepage = "https://pipewire.org"
documentation = "https://pipewire.pages.freedesktop.org/pipewire-rs/libspa_sys/"
keywords = [ "ffi", "pipewire", "multimedia", "audio", "video",]

[dependencies]

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"
system-deps = "6"

[lib]
doctest = false

[features]
v0_3_65 = []

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.69"
default-features = false
features = [ "experimental", "runtime",]

[package.metadata.system-deps.libspa]
name = "libspa-0.2"
version = "0.2"

[package.metadata.system-deps.libpipewire]
name = "libpipewire-0.3"
version = "0.3"

[[example]]
name = "vulkan"

[[example]]
name = "vulkan-android"
path = "examples/vulkan.rs"
crate-type = [ "cdylib",]

[package]
name = "openxr"
description = "High-level, mostly-safe OpenXR bindings"
repository = "https://github.com/Ralith/openxrs"
readme = "../README.md"
version = "0.19.0"
authors = [ "Benjamin Saunders <ben.e.saunders@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "api-bindings", "rendering",]
keywords = [ "vr",]
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"

[features]
static = [ "sys/static", "linked",]
loaded = [ "libloading",]
linked = [ "sys/linked",]
mint = [ "sys/mint",]
default = [ "loaded",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2.50"

[dev-dependencies]
ctrlc = "3.1.5"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "experimental"

[dependencies.sys]
package = "openxr-sys"
path = "../sys"
version = "0.11.0"

[dependencies.libloading]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.ash]
version = "0.38"
default-features = false
features = [ "loaded",]

[package.metadata.android]
build_targets = [ "aarch64-linux-android",]
runtime_libs = "examples/libs"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies]
ndk-context = "0.1"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "linked", "loaded", "mint",]

[package.metadata.android.sdk]
min_sdk_version = 21
target_sdk_version = 30

[package.metadata.android.application.activity]
theme = "@android:style/Theme.Black.NoTitleBar.Fullscreen"
config_changes = "density|keyboard|keyboardHidden|navigation|orientation|screenLayout|screenSize|uiMode"
launch_mode = "singleTask"
orientation = "landscape"
resizeable_activity = "false"
[[package.metadata.android.application.activity.intent_filter]]
actions = [ "android.intent.action.MAIN",]
categories = [ "com.oculus.intent.category.VR", "android.intent.category.LAUNCHER",]

[package]
name = "openxr-sys"
description = "OpenXR FFI bindings"
repository = "https://github.com/Ralith/openxrs"
readme = "../README.md"
version = "0.11.0"
authors = [ "Benjamin Saunders <ben.e.saunders@gmail.com>",]
categories = [ "external-ffi-bindings", "rendering",]
keywords = [ "openxr", "vr",]
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"
links = "openxr_loader"

[features]
linked = []
static = [ "cmake", "linked",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2.50"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "experimental"

[dependencies.mint]
version = "0.5.3"
optional = true

[build-dependencies.cmake]
version = "0.1.35"
optional = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "linked", "mint",]

[package]
name = "ovr_overlay"
version = "0.0.0"
description = "Rust bindings for OpenVR overlays"
authors = [ "Ryan Butler <thebutlah@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/TheButlah/ovr_overlay"
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = [ "ovr_applications", "ovr_chaperone_setup", "ovr_compositor", "ovr_input", "ovr_settings", "ovr_system",]
ovr_applications = []
ovr_chaperone_setup = []
ovr_compositor = []
ovr_input = []
ovr_system = []
ovr_settings = []

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1"
thiserror = "1"
derive_more = "0.99"
log = "0.4"
slice-of-array = "0.3"
enumset = "1.0.12"
byteorder = "1.4.3"

[workspace]
members = [ "sys",]
resolver = "2"

[dependencies.ovr_overlay_sys]
version = "=0.0.0"
path = "sys"

[dependencies.nalgebra]
version = "0.33"
optional = true

[package]
name = "ovr_overlay_sys"
version = "0.0.0"
description = "Rust low-level bindings for OpenVR overlays"
authors = [ "Ryan Butler <thebutlah@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/TheButlah/ovr_overlay"
edition = "2021"
exclude = [ "/openvr", "!/openvr/headers/openvr.h", "!/openvr/bin/win64/openvr_api.dll", "!/openvr/lib/win64/openvr_api.lib", "!/openvr/bin/linux64/libopenvr_api.so", "!/openvr/bin/linux32/libopenvr_api.so", "!/openvr/bin/linuxarm64/libopenvr_api.so", "!/openvr/bin/androidarm64/libopenvr_api.so",]

[dependencies]
autocxx = "0.27"
cxx = "1"

[build-dependencies]
autocxx-build = "0.27"
normpath = "1.2.0"
pkg-config = "0.3.31"

[package]
name = "pipewire"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Tom Wagner <tom.a.wagner@protonmail.com", "Guillaume Desmottes <guillaume.desmottes@collabora.com>",]
rust-version = "1.77"
edition = "2021"
categories = [ "api-bindings", "multimedia",]
description = "Rust bindings for PipeWire"
repository = "https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/pipewire/pipewire-rs"
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
homepage = "https://pipewire.org"
documentation = "https://pipewire.pages.freedesktop.org/pipewire-rs/pipewire/"
keywords = [ "pipewire", "multimedia", "audio", "video",]

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
thiserror = "1"
libc = "0.2"
bitflags = "2"
once_cell = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
once_cell = "1.5"

[features]
v0_3_32 = []
v0_3_33 = [ "spa/v0_3_33", "v0_3_32",]
v0_3_34 = [ "v0_3_33",]
v0_3_39 = [ "v0_3_34",]
v0_3_40 = [ "v0_3_39",]
v0_3_41 = [ "v0_3_40",]
v0_3_43 = [ "v0_3_41",]
v0_3_44 = [ "v0_3_43",]
v0_3_45 = [ "v0_3_44",]
v0_3_49 = [ "v0_3_45",]
v0_3_53 = [ "v0_3_49",]
v0_3_57 = [ "v0_3_53",]
v0_3_64 = [ "v0_3_57",]
v0_3_65 = [ "spa/v0_3_65", "v0_3_64",]
v0_3_77 = [ "v0_3_65",]

[dependencies.pw_sys]
package = "pipewire-sys"
version = "0.8"
path = "../pipewire-sys"

[dependencies.spa_sys]
package = "libspa-sys"
version = "0.8"
path = "../libspa-sys"

[dependencies.spa]
package = "libspa"
version = "0.8"
path = "../libspa"

[dependencies.nix]
version = "0.27"
features = [ "signal", "fs",]

[dev-dependencies.clap]
version = "4.3.2"
features = [ "derive",]

[package]
name = "pipewire-sys"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Tom Wagner <tom.a.wagner@protonmail.com", "Guillaume Desmottes <guillaume.desmottes@collabora.com>",]
rust-version = "1.77"
edition = "2021"
links = "pipewire-0.3"
categories = [ "api-bindings", "multimedia",]
description = "Rust FFI bindings for PipeWire"
repository = "https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/pipewire/pipewire-rs"
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
homepage = "https://pipewire.org"
documentation = "https://pipewire.pages.freedesktop.org/pipewire-rs/pipewire_sys/"
keywords = [ "ffi", "pipewire", "multimedia", "audio", "video",]

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "6"

[lib]
doctest = false

[dependencies.spa_sys]
package = "libspa-sys"
version = "0.8"
path = "../libspa-sys"

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.69"
default-features = false
features = [ "runtime",]

[package.metadata.system-deps.libpipewire]
name = "libpipewire-0.3"
version = "0.3"

[package]
name = "wayvr_ipc"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
bytes = "1.9.0"
smallvec = "1.13.2"
anyhow = "1.0.93"
log = "0.4.22"
serde_json = "1.0.135"

[features]
default = [ "client",]
client = [ "dep:tokio", "dep:tokio-util", "dep:interprocess",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.interprocess]
version = "2.2.2"
features = [ "tokio",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.42.0"
features = [ "macros",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7.13"
optional = true

[package]
name = "wlx-capture"
version = "0.5.3"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "galister",]
description = "Screen capture library for Wayland and X11"
repository = "https://github.com/galister/wlx-capture"
keywords = [ "desktop", "capture", "pipewire", "wayland", "x11",]
categories = [ "computer-vision", "multimedia::images",]
documentation = "https://docs.rs/wlx-capture"
license = "GPL-3.0"

[features]
default = [ "wayland", "pipewire",]
egl = []
wlr = [ "wayland",]
pipewire = [ "wayland", "dep:ashpd", "dep:pipewire",]
wayland = [ "dep:smithay-client-toolkit", "dep:wayland-client", "dep:wayland-protocols",]
xshm = [ "dep:rxscreen",]

[dependencies]
drm-fourcc = "2.2.0"
idmap = "0.2.21"
libc = "0.2.171"
log = "0.4.27"

[dependencies.ashpd]
version = "0.11.0"
default_features = false
features = [ "async-std",]
optional = true

[dependencies.pipewire]
git = "https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/galister/pipewire-rs.git"
ref = "ba32202c3c391004c3bb533b58fa75a50e47ff57"
features = [ "v0_3_33",]
optional = true

[dependencies.rxscreen]
version = "0.1.7"
features = [ "shm", "xrandr", "mouse",]
optional = true

[dependencies.smithay-client-toolkit]
version = "0.19.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.wayland-client]
version = "0.31.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.wayland-protocols]
version = "0.32.6"
features = [ "wayland-client", "client", "staging", "unstable",]
optional = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/galister/pipewire-rs"]
git = "https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/galister/pipewire-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/ralith/openxrs"]
git = "https://github.com/ralith/openxrs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "6c7747aee678048642dc16aad8bab3d6961dce03"

[source."https://github.com/galister/ovr_overlay_oyasumi"]
git = "https://github.com/galister/ovr_overlay_oyasumi"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/olekolek1000/wayvr-ipc"]
git = "https://github.com/olekolek1000/wayvr-ipc"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "a72587d23f3bb8624d9aeb1f13c0a21e65350f51"

[source."https://github.com/galister/wlx-capture"]
git = "https://github.com/galister/wlx-capture"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
tag = "v0.5.3"
